			<p>Although ObamaCare does a lot right, it also has consequences that affect specific groups of Americans. Since ObamaCare has hurt a number of small businesses, has negatively impacted insurance premiums, and has enacted reforms that hurt some medical industries and workers, I believe it should be repealed.</p>
